item.title: CVE-2020-25658|2024-08-04T15:40:36.903Z -- sybren%20a.%20st%C3%BCvel -- python-rsa
item.description: It was found that python-rsa is vulnerable to Bleichenbacher timing attacks. An attacker can use this flaw via the RSA decryption API to decrypt parts of the cipher text encrypted with RSA.
